strings:
<voice_0x01001C9D><se_high>Princess Medea: You know, it feels like ages since we last
came here.
<voice_0x01001C9E><se_high>Princess Medea: I want you to know how much I appreciate your hard work trying to lift the curse, <hero>.

<voice_0x01001C9F><se_high>Princess Medea: How are you feeling?
You must be exhausted.
<voice_0x01001CA0><se_high>Princess Medea: I want you to know that... Well, I would understand if you decided to give up.
<voice_0x01001CA1><se_high>Princess Medea: Why do I say that? Well, my father told me something the other day.
<voice_0x01001CA2><se_high>Princess Medea: He said that you have your own life to lead. That it wouldn't be right for us to drag you along with us for the rest of your life.
<voice_0x01001CA3><se_high>Princess Medea: You've done so much for us already. I promise I would never think badly of you if you decided to leave and go your own way.
